        "content": "<p>pchickey opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13170\">PR #13170</a> from <code>pchickey:wizer_improve_panic_message</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Improve the panic message that occurs when encountering a wizer bug such as #13168.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Instead of printing the wat of a very large component to stderr, write it to a file if above an arbitrary threshold (16k).</li>\n<li>Include context about the assertion in the panic message, rather than relying on the backtrace.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
